data.description: Fixer Upper!  1/2 acre lot backs up to the acequia in lovely Bosque Farms. Visionaries will appreciate the well built structure and grace of this once elegant ranch style home. Bring your imagination, tool box and ideas!Quiet neighborhood off the beaten path yet close enough to everything! 3bedrooms and 2 baths +unfiniished 1/4 bath off the mud room. Amazing stacked stone fireplace nods to finer days and cozy nights. 2 wells for irrigation. City water and sewer. Pro panel roof in 2023!Price reflects condition of home and is well below comparable homes.Absolutely no repairs will be done. Home is in Active Forclosure .Home is as-is! Inspections for info only.
